article.headline: Assura says rent collections continues normally
article.body: Assura PLC said Wednesday that rent collections in the first half have been in line with normal patterns and that it has disposed of 26 assets in the period for 23 million pounds ($29.6 million). The primary care property investor and developer also said it has an immediate development pipeline worth GBP65 million, which it expects to be on site within 12 months.
